{"tid":2377281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西醫工會幹事會6名成員集體辭職，不滿選舉涉嫌不公","createTime":"2021-01-23T12:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T16:21:11.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2846117066fbb2ef57c1a8e1f92f82e8b735a9cd","tid":2377281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T12:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/I_rlO63W1sZIVGos_L2W7Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcwNA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/1hgOhr9gZCWNMc06vAKU_A--~B/aD01NzI7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/e35fbd29f8167d7816edc79c03fc41e7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FI_rlO63W1sZIVGos_L2W7Q--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcwNA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F1hgOhr9gZCWNMc06vAKU_A--~B%2FaD01NzI7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fe35fbd29f8167d7816edc79c03fc41e7&h=7a1acabd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西醫工會早前被揭涉嫌選舉不公，爆出授權票風波。工會幹事會6名成員今日（23日）發出聯合聲明，指因不滿工會處理幹事會新選舉方案的手法，決定集體辭職。有份辭任的會董陸偉亮表示，工會在去年11月19日舉行周年大會，當時工會會長楊超發，以無法認證所有授權票為由，強行終止周年大會，惟在場的律師提出可以審視無效授權票亦不獲理會，認為選舉存有不公。東網向楊超發查詢，對方指「會內的事無可奉告，多謝關心。」<br />\n<br />\n陸偉亮指，2019年西醫工會幹事會選舉已涉嫌選舉不公，他憶述，當年11月幹事會選舉前夕，工會向會員發予授權票，惟該票上已預印了楊超發的名字，令楊選舉當日持有的授權票高達近70%。其後，成員亦揭工會成立18年來沒有進行過全面的內部審核、財務審核、報稅和交稅，據陸了解，稅務局已立案調查。<br />\n<br />\n延至去年11月，工會舉行新一屆周年大會選舉，最後採用新的郵寄投票方案，取代原有投票方式。陸偉亮質疑，做法無謹守會章以及職工會條例，並不同意處理方法。他又指，職工會登記局已經去信提醒工會，惟部份幹事會成員置之不理，故6名成員經討論後辭去幹事會所有職務。<br />\n<br />\n其他辭職成員還包括：會董梁漢輝、陳培光、任俊彥、胡志和及張允傑。"},{"pid":"bf74758d0cfd1e3f80799bead8d47d7f61514610","tid":2377281,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:00:16.000Z","msg":"可以爆大鑊了"},{"pid":"6d94022b86b1b80aa04c16d855c8b9b5dbc05c6a","tid":2377281,"uid":289775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11929528cc89d96d11042010a214a0d758e9472e","tid":2377281,"uid":38316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:48:39.000Z","msg":"中共鬥死埋西醫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下一步會定護士定老師？"},{"pid":"51a035e58e34393868a138dbb905ec7fcbb1717b","tid":2377281,"uid":73092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:55:01.000Z","msg":"2021年啦<br />\n仲相信選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53ccbefb35e0e4783ae9a3d5889dbfab937f716","tid":2377281,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:56:42.000Z","msg":"Stuff the ballot box !!"},{"pid":"62c874bf5854bdc2f5025d979c4c7fbaef90d4ce","tid":2377281,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c2f872c265d7358d6519df3a73376370d2dbc6","tid":2377281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62c874bf5854bdc2f5025d979c4c7fbaef90d4ce","tid":2377281,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T15:57:30.000Z","msg":"藍"},{"pid":"1ec9beaefa71455dff1f8570947c06eb153ab77e","tid":2377281,"uid":6497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62c874bf5854bdc2f5025d979c4c7fbaef90d4ce","tid":2377281,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:02:45.000Z","msg":"//成立「反港獨西醫前線」\t改<br />\n楊超發喺2016年曾經成立「反港獨西醫前線」，並以「反港獨、反壟斷、衹對事、不對人、愛中國、護香港」為參選口號。[1][2]<br />\n<br />\n反送中運動期間表現\t改<br />\n蘋果日報 9 月一篇報導入面，披露楊超發喺西醫工會嘅內部錄音，佢形容「反送中」事件係「暴動，嗰時四圍都有炸彈，又堵路呀嗰啲」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，立場新聞喺2020年11月報道，佢曾經至少兩次參加反送中遊行，同其他遊行人士一樣著黑衫、掛上白絲帶。立場新聞又獲得多張佢嘅自拍照片。立場新聞之後向楊超發查詢，佢就話有啲遊行有參加，有啲無，又話唔想講政治嘅嘢。有熟悉楊超發嘅西醫工會會員就批評，楊超發嘅做法係「食兩家茶禮」、「騎牆派」，對佢嘅舉動感到莫名其妙。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%A5%8A%E8%B6%85%E7%99%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25A5%258A%25E8%25B6%2585%25E7%2599%25BC&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2Takx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=d3c87e3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%A5%8A%E8%B6%85%E7%99%BC</a>"},{"pid":"07f25bfbd05fe45bbf230848fd43b62627807297","tid":2377281,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:06:19.000Z","msg":"藍絲工會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9292c28fc88f3dd3d488643bc3d6fbd90291ed1e","tid":2377281,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51a035e58e34393868a138dbb905ec7fcbb1717b","tid":2377281,"uid":73092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:55:01.000Z","msg":"2021年啦<br />\n仲相信選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:15:10.000Z","msg":"有票唔投 = 益建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb42b8730857895f8a9b2f542ce3a63416be5aa7","tid":2377281,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"07f25bfbd05fe45bbf230848fd43b62627807297","tid":2377281,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:06:19.000Z","msg":"藍絲工會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:18:58.000Z","msg":"自從蔡堅講咗句「特首唔同」之後<br />\n<br />\nCCTVB就只係訪問西醫工會<br />\n<br />\n唔訪問醫學會"},{"pid":"df1a61140cd38c6a606f9655503a0f50507fff26","tid":2377281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e